{"tid":999104,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"環保撚的電車難題","createTime":"2019-01-28T12:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T12:48:42.000Z","uid":199260,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a993b592ffadf8934b482ecc2ea200d1a25595","tid":999104,"uid":199260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的，假設你見到一架煞車壞咗嘅有軌電車，即將撞上前方軌道上嘅五個人，而旁邊的備用軌道上，有一個好特別嘅機關，當電車經過時會將1000枝飲管射入海中。如果你咩都唔做，五個人就會被撞死。你手邊有一個掣/手把，撳掣/拉下手把，車會駛入呢條備用軌道，只將1000枝飲管射入海中，而包括你在內嘅六個人都執唔返呢1000條飲管。你是否會犧牲海龜嘅鼻鼻而拯救另外五個人呢？<br />\n<br />\n延伸問題：<br />\n如果個機關射1000枝飲管就會拉手把/撳掣(去救五個人)，咁10000枝又拉唔拉/撳唔撳呢？10001枝？10002枝？"},{"pid":"7cad86c01cff3e9ed46483564cf17408af5a15c4","tid":999104,"uid":118988,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:00:05.000Z","msg":"當然係唔拉，1000 枝飲管唔駛射落海，而世上亦會少5個人製造垃圾<br />\n係雙贏"},{"pid":"d36b94583036fbf29ad0d0403e64f8f08819c484","tid":999104,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7cad86c01cff3e9ed46483564cf17408af5a15c4","tid":999104,"uid":118988,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:00:05.000Z","msg":"當然係唔拉，1000 枝飲管唔駛射落海，而世上亦會少5個人製造垃圾<br />\n係雙贏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:01:33.000Z","msg":"符合道德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d797b4a3014da43d7b36a52f1fe76d63d94fb9f","tid":999104,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-N_RZJUAQY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-N_RZJUAQY4&d=A8Zcnrt5rgz9w9jc%2F8WURF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=2e53f740\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-N_RZJUAQY4</a>"},{"pid":"cd11356b2458dd5bccc0972d202358f06351e6e3","tid":999104,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"車689又唔洗射得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji